Mentor Graphics Board Finds Icahn’s $17-a-Share Offer Undervalues Company

-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 
2011-03-28T12:03:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/mentor-board-finds-icahn-s-17-a-share-offer-undervalues-company.html
Mentor Graphics Corp. (MENT)  said its
board had determined billionaire investor  Carl Icahn ’s $17-a-
share offer undervalues the company, and said it remains open to
opportunities to enhance shareholder value.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
